791
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Veli, ti je moja smasna osoba.

792
00:42:39,519 --> 00:42:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je unutarnja inventura.

793
00:42:41,980 --> 00:42:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] A znajde, evo za kraj vidim.

794
00:42:44,039 --> 00:42:47,360
