798
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kupiš neku lijepu majcu

799
00:42:58,559 --> 00:43:02,280
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ti se ona zabije, onak, iza, s etiketom pazi.

800
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:05,780
