802
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, vidiš, to ti je.

803
00:43:10,199 --> 00:43:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ono kad naši 50 evra u dživu.

804
00:43:11,880 --> 00:43:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to ti je to, to ti je.

805
00:43:12,699 --> 00:43:15,019
[SPEAKER_01] To ti je inventura ormara i naših kapaciteta

806
00:43:15,019 --> 00:43:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] i taj put je baš super.

807
00:43:17,699 --> 00:43:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti, Ivona.

808
00:43:18,539 --> 00:43:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] A naše gledatelje također pozivamo da malo zavire u svojoj ormara

809
