837
00:44:35,559 --> 00:44:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] I nemojte pustiti ovo opet negdje sa strane.

838
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nego, evo, dignimo svi svoje živote na višu razinu.

839
00:44:41,119 --> 00:44:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] Do sljedećeg slušanja.

840
00:44:42,260 --> 00:44:42,760
